citations:
    citation-affc-samwell-iv:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Samwell IV"
            text_from_source: "The gates of the Citadel were flanked by a pair of towering green sphinxes with the bodies of lions, the wings of eagles, and the tails of serpents."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Sam arrives at the Citadel in Oldtown with Gilly and Dalla's babe. He meets Alleras (called the Sphinx, likely Sarella Sand in disguise). He is taken to Archmaester Marwyn, who reveals the Citadel's hostility to magic and dragons, and announces he will sail for Daenerys. Sam also meets 'Pate' — actually Jaqen H'ghar in disguise, who murdered the real Pate in the AFFC prologue. Sam is assigned to help with the ravens."
